<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    
    <!-- the same applies to the rest of the code. The elemets that I've already declare that are comming form the template are similar below-->
    
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />

    <title><%= yield(:title) %>About Us</title>


    <meta content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0' name='viewport' />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

    <!-- Bootstrap core CSS     -->
    <link href="assets/stylesheets/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Animation library for notifications   -->
    <link href="assets/stylesheets/animate.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!--  Light Bootstrap Table core CSS    -->
    <link href="assets/stylesheets/light-bootstrap-dashboard.css?v=1.4.0" rel="stylesheet">


    <!--     Fonts and icons     -->
    <link href="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.2.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,700,300" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="assets/stylesheets/pe-icon-7-stroke.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.0.1/jquery.min.jsy">
    
    <!-- need it for icons-->
    <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.2.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

</head>
<body>
   <%= render 'layouts/header' %>
   
   <div class="content purple-horizontal">
       <p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>
       <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="card card-plain">
                    <div class="header">
                        <h4 class="title">About Us</h4>
                        <p class="category">Who are we?</p>
                        <br>
                        <%= image_tag("vadim.jpg", :alt => "developer", :class => "portrait") %> 
                        <br>  <br>
                        <p>Greetings, my name is Vadim Malakhovski and I am the developer of this website.</p> 
                        <br>
                        <p>I wanted to create a simple website which would contain the best current TOP jockes from around the world.</p> 
                        <br>
                        <p> So why not just Googling a jocke?</p>
                         <br>
                        <p>There reason for this is that if you need few funny jockes you do not have to search for a funny jocke but just use this website. </p> 
                        <p>Also, later on, I would create functionality to vote for the jockes an in this way we can be sure that the website contains the funniest jockes.</p>
                        <br>
                        <!--change the link to heroku-->
                        <p>If you would like to post a jocke that you think is worthy to be on this website then please <a href="https://toptenjokes.herokuapp.com/contact">contact me</a>.</p>
                        <br>
                        <p>P.S. And remember that humor extends your lifespan</p> 
                        
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-------------------------------------------------------------------------------  All Students TABLE END------------------>       
                    


                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        



    </div>
</div>



<%= render 'layouts/footer' %>
</body>


<!--   Core JS Files   -->
<script src="assets/javascripts/jquery.3.2.1.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="assets/javascripts/bootstrap.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

